# LogChain

Tamper-proof server logs on Solana.

## Problem
Server logs can be changed after a breach. No proof of integrity.

## Solution
- Hash every log line  
- Build Merkle tree (100 entries)  
- Anchor root on Solana  
- Tamper = broken chain = proof

## Demo
[https://logchain.vercel.app](https://logchain.vercel.app) *(devnet)*

## Tech
- **Off-chain**: Node.js + `merkletreejs`  
- **On-chain**: Anchor (Rust)  
- **Frontend**: React + `@solana/web3.js`

